{"title":"蔷薇小集——少年运动会的短诗","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":9,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔷薇小集"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——少年运动会的短诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扇子操"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一群蝴蝶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着北京的花香飞来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻地落在花丛上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风又向草地飞去……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞在山泉一样的音乐里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞在人们的微笑中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射箭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这支箭还带着草原的气息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从姑娘的指缝间射出去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调皮的海风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕你吹呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声响，赞美像海潮袭来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘的笑脸是一朵芙蓉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞赛场上像伞兵刚刚挨着地面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像白绣球花刚刚开放。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在伞的旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鹰在翻腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在花的旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子在飞舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道看哪里好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里都是一幅画——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有最鲜艳的色彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的线条……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1956年8月于青岛"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}